Letters to the Editor:
   Help for Employers
   On Disabilities Rules
JAN has handled, during the past seven years, 29,000
cases. There are well over 20,000 accommodation "solutions"
in the system, with updated information constantly being
received from manufacturers and/or organizations. JAN's phone
number is 1800-JAN-7234. It also serves employers in Canada
through a separate contracted service at 1-800-JAN-CANA.
   Richard C. Douglas
   Executive Director
   President's Committee
   on Employment of People With Disabilities
   Washington